钙钛矿体系，结合缺陷工程、高熵化改性及理论模拟方法，系统揭示了通过A/B位离子设计与微观结构调控可有效提升其热膨胀系数、降低热导率并抑制高温相变。研究表明，改性后的锆酸盐钙钛矿热导率可降低约35%，且与YSZ具备良好化学相容性。该综述为航空发动机、燃气轮机等热端部件在更高温环境下的涂层选材与工艺开发提供了材料设计与性能优化的重要参考。",RECID:"R4P1A1091EBB959102"},{FN:"RPTJ202501003",pushStartTime:"2026-02-05 00:00:00",TI:"大气等离子喷涂热障涂层界面设计及寿命优化研究进展",ABSTRACTUrl:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/article/abstract?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck1H-diRC0pbHQW_JFdSXpivJIzc5XWLrWHjZ5RJFg10y_aYye1da1VaKG-msolGjtCpvRd_xyo6jmyoh0JzxwZnbjeR2YHPvK4NwdH9UZrLCJCm7gfeBp4ib4vpuO9nllgFo4DLrXIRbmf4aPyF5WN3u3ZKO3aNlCgni4VSQ4cpo9wV7MpjT7_NLllsDpEsB0Q=&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS",AUTHORS:[{no:1,id:"000003516025",title:"罗丽荣",aff:[1],email:"",corresponding:!1,role:null,equalau:null,relations:[{scope:"ABSTRACT",url:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/author/detail?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck19cPg7TG_ogMUEJqre3uSyuv1pwReRIR7RCbZyGOB5zXWADFi3ZhTL4aZCH49zoP4bsmGbVczWcUrxN78NmTK3317x03EsXT34jbLvsuLWXKCzv8wrS7Tf&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS"}],ABSTRACTUrl:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/author/detail?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck19cPg7TG_ogMUEJqre3uSyuv1pwReRIR7RCbZyGOB5zXWADFi3ZhTL4aZCH49zoP4bsmGbVczWcUrxN78NmTK3317x03EsXT34jbLvsuLWXKCzv8wrS7Tf&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS"},{no:2,id:"000037522567",title:"陆杰",aff:[1],email:"",corresponding:!1,role:null,equalau:null,relations:[{scope:"ABSTRACT",url:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/author/detail?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck19cPg7TG_ogMUEJqre3uSy-8pLj7reRsRa3lkos1nP3Ir09BsUe7dl1_b6z87KSPg9AEnARZVIc9Aw5lDG6-lcK-SPtqxbGpCRHP0HtdEt3g==&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS"}],ABSTRACTUrl:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/author/detail?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck19cPg7TG_ogMUEJqre3uSy-8pLj7reRsRa3lkos1nP3Ir09BsUe7dl1_b6z87KSPg9AEnARZVIc9Aw5lDG6-lcK-SPtqxbGpCRHP0HtdEt3g==&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS"},{no:3,id:"000013548839",title:"蔡黄越",aff:[1],email:"",corresponding:!1,role:null,equalau:null,relations:[{scope:"ABSTRACT",url:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/author/detail?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck19cPg7TG_ogMUEJqre3uSy5y1O1jQfOkxb4DSqnHGwOwwPp7By9GDFqlZl5fL7LUk2mZSV0c_fQia-c9sjLjxiN4zg9_Y5mXCMqO_J79kRq357HDPEZkm7&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=