究对象，依托自制磁化装置与可视化试验系统，系统探究不同磁感应强度磁化处理对浮选气泡速度、变形、兼并及跳动等关键运动行为的调控规律，精准识别各药剂体系适配的最优磁化参数，首次发现油酸钠体系气泡上升速度的双峰值独特特征。研究试验设计严谨，数据支撑充分，明晰了磁化作用与浮选药剂体系的耦合效应，从气泡运动微观层面揭示磁化强化浮选的作用机制，为磁化技术在浮选工艺中的精准优化与工程化应用提供重要试验依据和理论支撑，兼具显著的学术价值与工程实践指导意义。",RECID:"R4P1A1091EBB959114"},{FN:"YSXK202407009",pushStartTime:"2026-01-24 00:00:00",TI:"基于电感式传感器阵列成像的废金属识别方法",ABSTRACTUrl:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/article/abstract?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck3YoiaRkHs4m5c8MljaDJ01YbICB1n1UL0zu-yZWM2lNbjSwEA8VRT1TTKVTPHzeEnwatJhmIBVsL3wO-kwURtmttWqf8uj9tSzBZptUYQ_xu-wgd1xcb2RBBpSitBKwOvGn-42IWpSIrjjcsphY3f6U46R6OsDK4GCgJOegOdu72gVfFFldBUr-IuuulPRMOE=&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS",AUTHORS:[{no:1,id:"000050407627",title:"张朝宏",aff:[1],email:"",corresponding:!1,role:null,equalau:null,relations:[{scope:"ABSTRACT",url:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/author/detail?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck3YoiaRkHs4mxn-z2-wOH8iX10dbn39KiCmcJBjSqH8m587WqLJyueXzODoXq5V9un5wAhg73n4CM0_PDd41xBR40m98eQdueOv4XcNv-IvB34DaCv2Lora&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS"}],ABSTRACTUrl:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/author/detail?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck3YoiaRkHs4mxn-z2-wOH8iX10dbn39KiCmcJBjSqH8m587WqLJyueXzODoXq5V9un5wAhg73n4CM0_PDd41xBR40m98eQdueOv4XcNv-IvB34DaCv2Lora&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS"},{no:2,id:"000040717841",title:"叶文华",aff:[1],email:"",corresponding:!0,role:null,equalau:null,relations:[{scope:"ABSTRACT",url:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/author/detail?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck3YoiaRkHs4mxn-z2-wOH8iQn4wgQlw3_B-RbwsDdb10W5Tdp15b3JQECqrX39X0ni0zk8TjZZI8PCxrmkf_RUKYrwNx3hCkDG_hcN_F66Htle3fu04WMKV&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS"}],ABSTRACTUrl:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/author/detail?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck3YoiaRkHs4mxn-z2-wOH8iQn4wgQlw3_B-RbwsDdb10W5Tdp15b3JQECqrX39X0ni0zk8TjZZI8PCxrmkf_RUKYrwNx3hCkDG_hcN_F66Htle3fu04WMKV&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS"},{no:3,id:"000045703607",title:"周亚楠",aff:[1],email:"",corresponding:!1,role:null,equalau:null,relations:[{scope:"ABSTRACT",url:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/author/detail?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck3YoiaRkHs4mxn-z2-wOH8iCjZfS9n1YM9ynhtI0NXJcYS6xADxO4wRII2_jEiS-lN1e6T9MsMvB2Y1g