25",QI:"04",PT:"2025-03-13 21:09",DFR:"412",recommendPerson:"朱阳戈",recommendPersonPosition:"执行主编",recommendReason:"    研磨是多行业核心工序，却存在高能耗、高材耗痛点，研磨电耗占比高，降耗提效已成行业迫切需求，而添加助磨剂是最有效手段之一。本文系统梳理助磨剂发展历程，分类介绍有机、无机常用助磨剂种类，综述其改变化物料性、促进颗粒分散等作用机理研究现状，以及在矿物加工、水泥等行业的应用实践。同时分析物料性质、用量、研磨条件等对助磨剂效能的影响，剖析各行业应用现存问题，展望未来发展趋势。研究为各行业助磨剂科学选型提供参考，也为研磨工序降耗提效、降低生产成本提供了实用方法与理论借鉴，兼具行业指导与实践应用价值。",RECID:"R4P1A1091EBB959113"},{FN:"YSKU202501015",pushStartTime:null,TI:"大型露天矿采场边坡安全监测综合预警平台搭建与应用",ABSTRACTUrl:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/article/abstract?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck0G0y5Kk70hRg9crXui-LydaJf1BEnA3J6vdRIRZDPfRoAkhUlozuEf1HROBwQgkxjrsFI5sjxYAwChHUjMldqQA9wOouPQpn80M1lO2VPBBnuSRBG_cZWciMDNqyrPY-ILoOkSSCM394mqk1a7qlBVBds01qS8KBXHGUZ6wQZveOyPXTh3pEsjmXHVSdJpSWs=&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS",AUTHORS:[{no:1,id:"000006103618",title:"郭子林",aff:[1],email:"",corresponding:!1,role:null,equalau:null,relations:[{scope:"ABSTRACT",url:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/author/detail?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck0G0y5Kk70hRh8fvpsC192slDKxnpl3_A4QP74YvK0c_yOJ2v4_Nx5ohLgSP66iUfnOwXrZVY6vXqdVISdjjab0XWXXLvUkk7wNXzkfPAllqjTMglh3tKzs&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS"}],ABSTRACTUrl:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/author/detail?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck0G0y5Kk70hRh8fvpsC192slDKxnpl3_A4QP74YvK0c_yOJ2v4_Nx5ohLgSP66iUfnOwXrZVY6vXqdVISdjjab0XWXXLvUkk7wNXzkfPAllqjTMglh3tKzs&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS"},{no:2,id:"000056976419",title:"吴琼",aff:[1],email:"",corresponding:!0,role:null,equalau:null,relations:[{scope:"ABSTRACT",url:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/author/detail?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck0G0y5Kk70hRh8fvpsC192sV3oIuvG5aSkOnLcp_FBIcrAK08tPGLNCpFO_2a5mKdftKQ6GN-Q1LGt5ZmmgEuQ0TB4BgDFRkA8NknBpPHMIsQ==&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS"}],ABSTRACTUrl:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/author/detail?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck0G0y5Kk70hRh8fvpsC192sV3oIuvG5aSkOnLcp_FBIcrAK08tPGLNCpFO_2a5mKdftKQ6GN-Q1LGt5ZmmgEuQ0TB4BgDFRkA8NknBpPHMIsQ==&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS"},{no:3,id:"000024886488",title:"闫宝军",aff:[1],email:"",corresponding:!1,role:null,equalau:null,relations:[{scope:"ABSTRACT",url:"https://kns.cnki.net