ER",url:"https://c61.cnki.net/cjfd/small/wjfx.jpg"}],PUBLICATIONUrl:"https://navi.cnki.net/knavi/detail?p=JdAw85JOJMImrXPd7krnxXlGqwEh8jsbUWcxIS4JpfnSjI0gwaCAjFofbZ-KFDafCk6tBTbCouiK9Dpcoz61HVEhKinNnGT7rV2q49VCL7c=&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS",ISSUEUrl:"https://navi.cnki.net/knavi/detail?p=JdAw85JOJMImrXPd7krnxXlGqwEh8jsbtju8gRCrdaBcTHonqoXCo2aLtKK569xt1wzpzrWSN0QP4686t298bbH0vB77bejObd3RK96ZjyanosnQXC-oIC2quFiQsc9t&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS",COVERUrl:"https://c61.cnki.net/cjfd/small/wjfx.jpg"},YE:"2025",QI:"11",PT:"2025-09-04 09:07",DFR:"347",recommendPerson:"章连香",recommendPersonPosition:"执行主编",recommendReason:"本文系统阐述了同步辐射红外光源的特点、相关仪器及实验发展现状及技术应用。利用同步辐射产生的高亮度红外光，在材料、能源、生物、环境、乃至考古等领域，揭开一个又一个肉眼不可见的科学奥秘。论文数据显示，在5μm的小孔下，它比常规光源亮几十倍，信噪比极佳。同步辐射红外光谱正在电池界面寻找失效原因、土壤颗粒中追踪污染物、单根蚕丝里分析蛋白质结构等领域寻找纳米级的化学证据。“未来，通过与人工智能、扫描探针等技术的深度融合，这台‘超级化学显微镜’将看得更细（纳米级）、懂得更深（智能解析）、环境更真（多场调控）。它将继续作为探索物质微观世界的‘慧眼’，推动从基础科学到产业创新的跨越。”",RECID:"R4P1A1091EBB959115"},{FN:"YSKU202502017",pushStartTime:null,TI:"多手段的空场法采空区隐蔽致灾因素普查技术与应用",ABSTRACTUrl:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/article/abstract?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck1nCNZw79ElDj6e17FRZexL2FfZIuB1r63mrgDqxA1r55JY2oW5aSRMNif-Mf6eBxIU0AM2oBnXZQvImAY_2Qv8HOpE9nSaY3D5xG3w7FD49CtqSp9O_Jrvi7SNhk4SoR20T88icBNl9lfTEvDJe4xEZWkLB2b6WWm7s7Kzs_XscoyPqBpoyiX807nASVlgV7s=&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS",AUTHORS:[{no:1,id:"000054470755",title:"甄智鑫",aff:[1,2],email:"",corresponding:!1,role:null,equalau:null,relations:[{scope:"ABSTRACT",url:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/author/detail?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck1nCNZw79ElDpNZSOjeWhyjD8tZk6QcvJQK4n3BXwNMR76ScF_5V_OR33xGlJhhdX3k_7JsXpD1x86oQTjJM7MkbtdUtPCR030U6H9i7YJbXCkxhkEBdKbd&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS"}],ABSTRACTUrl:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/author/detail?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck1nCNZw79ElDpNZSOjeWhyjD8tZk6QcvJQK4n3BXwNMR76ScF_5V_OR33xGlJhhdX3k_7JsXpD1x86oQTjJM7MkbtdUtPCR030U6H9i7YJbXCkxhkEBdKbd&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS"},{no:2,id:"000004707936",title:"孟磊磊",aff:[3],email:"",corresponding:!1,role:null,equalau:null,relations:[{scope:"ABSTRACT",url:"h