",COVERUrl:"https://c61.cnki.net/cjfd/small/ysxk.jpg"},YE:"2025",QI:"07",PT:"2025-07-02 14:01",DFR:"197",recommendPerson:"朱阳戈",recommendPersonPosition:"执行主编",recommendReason:"针对湖北宜昌某低品位高镁胶磷矿，为高效脱镁提质，本文采用改性脂肪酸捕收剂E-2与磷酸抑制剂，系统优化磨矿细度、药剂制度及浮选流程并开展开闭路试验。确定磨矿细度-0.074 mm占72.58%，可实现矿物解离且避免过磨问题；弱酸性介质中E-2对白云石吸附性最佳，粗选E-2 0.8 kg/t+磷酸8 kg/t浮选效果最优。采用“一粗一精两扫”流程，开路试验尾矿P₂O₅降至5.07%；闭路试验在优化药剂用量下，获P₂O₅品位30.91%、MgO 0.89%、回收率93.71%精矿，镁脱除率达86.69%。该工艺兼顾高脱镁率与高磷回收率，为同类型高镁磷矿开发提供技术参考。",RECID:"R4P1A1091EBB959123"},{FN:"RPTJ202501002",pushStartTime:null,TI:"钙钛矿热障材料的研究进展",ABSTRACTUrl:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/article/abstract?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck2UWjxoM7j2op7ws0_vunv2yGyc8Qb9PXkoLloTNoDGXWZ66SjVdO0HmjnVAXMdQoSMNDiJUXRkH02L99PPWC6fwb5aD4ja-Q0UrwMA8ssWVnHWCzIgQfc_AYjFLcQcUjPzZm4Q98tKlwpbKVkSFz2PyZJXG1oP8kpaXvAB_k7qPGKRuWFUEKxsLELneMZx6T0=&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS",AUTHORS:[{no:1,id:"000068556553",title:"程厚燕",aff:[1,2],email:"",corresponding:!1,role:null,equalau:null,relations:[{scope:"ABSTRACT",url:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/author/detail?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck2UWjxoM7j2ogEaDGlvY7W2cquLKidQDqfbRQ95qw7I-fbHFn2TjOyvpo9RSq-t1QVThgJaLj6f85ti3rGpvPJmKPN94P6nTZG_AmQyt8rgfnpeu0bJA3gl&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS"}],ABSTRACTUrl:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/author/detail?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck2UWjxoM7j2ogEaDGlvY7W2cquLKidQDqfbRQ95qw7I-fbHFn2TjOyvpo9RSq-t1QVThgJaLj6f85ti3rGpvPJmKPN94P6nTZG_AmQyt8rgfnpeu0bJA3gl&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS"},{no:2,id:"000016062454",title:"梁立康",aff:[1,2],email:"",corresponding:!1,role:null,equalau:null,relations:[{scope:"ABSTRACT",url:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/author/detail?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck2UWjxoM7j2ogEaDGlvY7W20Jr2MxNEF-RO2bYHSZVWfhhCfvEvibriQr09tFCpA5BDv3LhCz7FpSZOntwCawQig5cAxfJz046SdvRl0-ZDm25A1hM0dcm0&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS"}],ABSTRACTUrl:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/author/detail?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck2UWjxoM7j2ogEaDGlvY7W20Jr2MxNEF-RO2bYHSZVWfhhCfvEvibriQr09tFCpA5BDv3LhCz7FpSZOntwCawQig5cAxfJz046SdvRl0-ZDm25A1hM0dcm0&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS"},{no:3,id:"000071548451",title:"何箐",aff:[1,