过氧化增重测量与组织表征，系统揭示了涂层高温氧化的两阶段规律：初期形成针状Al₂O₃膜并快速增重，后期转为致密层状结构且氧化速率显著放缓。同时，定量测得涂层与基体间的元素互扩散系数约为3.0 μm/h，扩散层厚度随氧化时间呈平方根增长。该成果为航空发动机热端部件防护涂层的寿命预测与失效分析提供了关键的氧化动力学数据与界面行为依据；建议重点关注第2.2节氧化膜形貌演变与第2.3节扩散行为的定量分析",RECID:"R4P1A1091EBB959125"},{FN:"YSXK202502004",pushStartTime:null,TI:"氢键在非硫化矿浮选捕收剂吸附机理中的作用",ABSTRACTUrl:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/article/abstract?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck3FXqOH56Y-pIOISeC2xnGKmK3UbaBYGirT2XUbn1tvTQ1xnW54krOMikhCzAhEheUdOLRs_9QEQ2kZF1o2a_mcbMfYferUTiiG_ZqU6ui2C73w5tD8LChwFD5SjalKj1YEGiEC2opIBQrmL7scWwMopB1b5WYECoXGpUNOC0BLb9cQwVfptIshGlvnmT3-NL8=&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS",AUTHORS:[{no:1,id:"000039211202",title:"朱一民",aff:[1,2],email:"",corresponding:null,role:null,equalau:null,relations:[{scope:"ABSTRACT",url:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/author/detail?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck0HoOCAgD71-bZhYRy7eLCIVf4Tu7QaujPOEvSyC4XLZ2PppR8tY37UvQC3Ku_CgShhY01AJnZIgf7EZXzuX_SN78D65VRxVDtfNUs0Q4c-Kw6BWax-yfH8&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS"}],ABSTRACTUrl:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/author/detail?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck0HoOCAgD71-bZhYRy7eLCIVf4Tu7QaujPOEvSyC4XLZ2PppR8tY37UvQC3Ku_CgShhY01AJnZIgf7EZXzuX_SN78D65VRxVDtfNUs0Q4c-Kw6BWax-yfH8&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS"},{no:2,id:"000065152800",title:"乘舟越洋",aff:[1,3],email:"",corresponding:null,role:null,equalau:null,relations:[{scope:"ABSTRACT",url:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/author/detail?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck0HoOCAgD71-bZhYRy7eLCISUwwRSE6icfBLIPVgipDTMT4yUCEREuSRZvN2XG7XrKNXYQp7Ikp9qvAVh7CZkpqgOdk_p9CIPuD2ME4r2FRW-J8_Wrj6E_xPogES6AMGhw=&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS"}],ABSTRACTUrl:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/author/detail?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck0HoOCAgD71-bZhYRy7eLCISUwwRSE6icfBLIPVgipDTMT4yUCEREuSRZvN2XG7XrKNXYQp7Ikp9qvAVh7CZkpqgOdk_p9CIPuD2ME4r2FRW-J8_Wrj6E_xPogES6AMGhw=&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS"},{no:3,id:"000031301262",title:"刘杰",aff:[1,2],email:"",corresponding:null,role:null,equalau:null,relations:[{scope:"ABSTRACT",url:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/author/detail?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck0HoOCAgD71-bZhYRy7eLCI9MkBnqZEB043ZqFTMILXLkAUUItSssc0lwhUivKC5u49XQKxI-Xx7lg5mBshC