le:"有色金属(冶炼部分)",year:"2025",volume:"",issue:"12",relations:[{scope:"PUBLICATION",url:"https://navi.cnki.net/knavi/detail?p=JdAw85JOJMKF7Aglo1aJrXqmw3DEUlECUbFVAKiLotBn2ckjspuZgUgsEPvwP-DMXPYu-q1c3MsOtvoyCwfkyOZTJnujTlS9_XvFf2jv6vE=&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS"},{scope:"ISSUE",url:"https://navi.cnki.net/knavi/detail?p=JdAw85JOJMKF7Aglo1aJrXqmw3DEUlECGTjF7vNPEkUBcKTfiM-vEZC9f9zQfmnRf8_QxPa4_3MEdtBPW2VMLx3E2cTEds1KYig6CR7arg8dwDJf6PdvNqfQ8xtB6zg4&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS"},{scope:"COVER",url:"https://c61.cnki.net/cjfd/small/mete.jpg"}],PUBLICATIONUrl:"https://navi.cnki.net/knavi/detail?p=JdAw85JOJMKF7Aglo1aJrXqmw3DEUlECUbFVAKiLotBn2ckjspuZgUgsEPvwP-DMXPYu-q1c3MsOtvoyCwfkyOZTJnujTlS9_XvFf2jv6vE=&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS",ISSUEUrl:"https://navi.cnki.net/knavi/detail?p=JdAw85JOJMKF7Aglo1aJrXqmw3DEUlECGTjF7vNPEkUBcKTfiM-vEZC9f9zQfmnRf8_QxPa4_3MEdtBPW2VMLx3E2cTEds1KYig6CR7arg8dwDJf6PdvNqfQ8xtB6zg4&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS",COVERUrl:"https://c61.cnki.net/cjfd/small/mete.jpg"},YE:"2025",QI:"12",PT:"2025-12-02",DFR:"128",recommendPerson:"金开生",recommendPersonPosition:"执行主编",recommendReason:"电流强化是铝电解槽提产降本最直接、最有效的手段，但阳极电流分布不均带来的稳定性、能耗与安全隐忧始终制约其规模化应用。本文跳出了“就电流论电流”的传统框架，首次把阳极电流均匀性置于电场—磁场—热场—流场“多场耦合”的时空演化链条中，从机理、检测、调控到操作进行系统重构：提出“磁场自均衡+导流阳极+复合阴极+对称换极”四维协同理念，将电流分布从被动容忍转为主动设计；引入“新极回全”窗口期概念，使换极扰动由经验时段变为可控变量；把“强化—均流—节能—安全”由矛盾三角转化为兼容目标。工业验证表明，优化后的高电流强度槽可在不增加额外能耗与风险的前提下，实现平稳运行与清洁生产双赢。",RECID:"R4P1A1091EBB959129"},{FN:"RPTJ202501008",pushStartTime:null,TI:"高温合金薄壁构件Ar/He大气等离子喷涂单次预热的温度场和应力场数值研究",ABSTRACTUrl:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/article/abstract?v=Ap1IM-J3Ck2-6iPkPJoYWJ3zHfKkt7mc0K_JRCL04LJyUcScktWPi8r7rOmSlDidAFGxFdshvgfY3JmG-diB67ruTgTDrB7Fa6gssYW94SkpHITROVn40yAFVljZWNQirZVi7QMS5aOjAdbg8M6f4Mc5XI4A0eSg--00MacXOldioHejXrsWTopynIbVO0HYdbXwbAqpCAs=&uniplatform=NZKPT&language=CHS",AUTHORS:[{no:1,id:"000068556329",title:"雷一帆",aff:[1],email:"",corresponding:!1,role:null,equalau:null,relations:[{scope:"ABSTRACT",url:"https://kns.cnki.net/kcms2/author/detail?v=Ap1IM-J3C